data.text: I’m in a bad mood tonight. Rant over.
I’m all cool if you regret being in a film of his. Please just make it known before you try to hand out your faux-feminism to the world with your all black suits and fancy little pins.
EXCEPT for David Krumholtz who issued a wonderful apology for his appearance in WONDER WHEEL.

When will people stop working for him?

None of these people’s sentiments mean shit to me until they distance their involvement with the film. This also goes for everyone in WONDER WHEEL too.
